    Return true

Process called "separate_variables" that takes expr as SymCore.SymbolicExpression and dep_var as String and indep_var as String returns SeparatedForm:
    Note: Simplified variable separation
    Return SeparatedForm with:
        x_function as SymCore.create_symbol with name as indep_var
        y_function as SymCore.create_symbol with name as dep_var

Type called "SeparatedForm":
